Just for fun, a domain ticket.  Give 'em to folks whose servers don't
work.  This is a postscript document and revised copy of the one I
sent to the IETF.

Craig

--cut-here---

/box-10 {	% x y box
    newpath
    moveto
    0 10 rlineto
    10 0 rlineto
    0 -10 rlineto
    -10 0 rlineto
    stroke
} def

newpath
72 80 moveto
72 720 540 720 8 arcto 4 { pop } repeat
540 720 540 72 8 arcto 4 { pop } repeat
540 72 72 72 8 arcto 4 { pop } repeat
72 72 72 720 8 arcto 4 { pop } repeat
stroke

/Helvetica-Bold findfont 24 scalefont setfont
306 (Domain Name System Infraction) stringwidth pop 2 div sub 670 moveto
(Domain Name System Infraction) show

/Helvetica findfont 16 scalefont setfont
306 (DNS Inspection Services.  Dr. P.V. Mockapetris, Chief Inspector) stringwidth pop \
2 div sub 645 moveto (DNS Inspection Services.  Dr. P.V. Mockapetris, Chief \
Inspector) show

72 635 moveto
540 635 lineto
stroke

/Helvetica-Bold findfont 15 scalefont setfont
95 600 moveto
(IP Address of Offender:) show
5 0 rmoveto
108 0 rlineto
stroke

95 570 moveto
(Domain Name of Offender:) show
5 0 rmoveto
176 0 rlineto
stroke

72 550 moveto
540 550 lineto
stroke

